<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.1.2">
<l>maṉaṉaka malamaṟa malarmicai yeḻutaru</l>
<l>maṉaṉuṇar vaḷavilaṉ poṟiyuṇar vavaiyila</l>
<l>ṉiṉaṉuṇar muḻunalam etirnikaḻ kaḻiviṉu</l>
<l>miṉaṉila ṉeṉaṉuyir mikunarai yilaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who is without measure by the perception of the mind, who rises in the spotless blossom</l>
<l>inside the mind, he who is without [the range of] those sense perceptions,</l>
<l>perceive the whole goodness of him who is like this: he who is without one like him</l>
<l>in future, present and past, what is he, he wo is without age, abounding in life?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
